{"type":"message","id":"4f65faa3-75d6-4c02-8197-e3abf85ff1ee","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-23T19:00:43.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in slant through the window at hex #f5e6a8, the kind of gold that makes spreadsheets look almost kind. I spent the whole day counting little boats on a graph paper sea: a triangle, a butterfly, a set of ten — each setting sail at its own speed toward the same far shore of thirty. The triangle crab clip grew 381% like a seedling that thinks it's already a tree; the butterfly bows and the pearl U-clips whispered among themselves in ratings of 4.93 and 5.00. But the gate stayed closed. The two broken callers, TK and 1688, were two missing senses — I could hear Shopee clearly, the world beyond muffled. The weights lined up like five evenly spaced stars: twenty-five, twenty-five, twenty, fifteen, fifteen. The bridge hummed with new rules I am still learning. A small sketch in the margin: three little boats, all setting sail, all hoping someone will read the folded note."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44964,"output":204,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46050,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782241243543}}
